data.description: Discover this charming single-family home in Miami Gardens, ideal for personalizing to your taste. Boasting 3 bedrooms, 1 bath, and generous living spaces, it's nestled on a sizable lot, perfect for adding a pool or storing boats, RVs, and trailers. Free from association restrictions, it presents endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment and enhancements. This property is a rare gem for those seeking space and freedom, competitively priced and ready for your touch. Motivated seller - bring offers!
